{
  "title": "What Do We Know About the Link Between Marriage and Health?",
  "abstract": "This special journal issue presents nine new studies on the relationship between marriage and health among African Americans. It discusses health disparities between African Americans and other racial and ethnic groups, offers an overview of African American marriage rates, and presents evidence for the marriage-health link in this population.",
